articles.title: ICC announces prize money for India vs Australia WTC final winner and runners-up - Hindustan Times
articles.description: The India vs Australia WTC final winners will get a hefty some as prize money from ICC apart form the Test mace. | Cricket
articles.content: ICC on Friday announced the prize money for the winners and runner-ups of the World Test Championship final between India and Australia slated to be played at The Oval, England from June 7 to 11 with… [+2114 chars]
